@startuml
title Mention Handling with Memory Layer

start

:Receive @mention from user;

:Load conversation history\nfrom SQLite (user_id + channel_id);

if (History load succeeds?) then (yes)
  if (History has summary?) then (yes)
    :Inject summary + recent turns\ninto context;
  else (no)
    :Inject recent turns into context;
  endif
else (no)
  :Log warning, proceed\nwithout history;
  note right: Graceful degradation
endif

:Build messages:\nsystem_prompt (with memory)\n+ user_prompt (with history);

:Enter tool-call loop\n(existing mention.py logic);

:AI returns final response;

:Save conversation turn to SQLite\n(user msg + AI reply + tool summary);

if (Total turns > threshold?) then (yes)
  :Summarize oldest turns via AI;
  :Store summary, delete\nsummarized raw turns;
else (no)
endif

:Send response to Discord;

stop
@enduml
